title: Fisherman 4: Attack of the Hook
description: If you’re out past midnight, beware. The fisherman’s hook is waiting to drop in.
quote: Hey! My ice cream! No! It was Rocky Road!
altHero: view of a boat, fishing line, and hook from below the water’s surface
alt1: fish on a seesaw with a joyful open mouth, but a hook is about to hook him
alt2: couple on a bench and the boy fish has a hook pulling his pants upward
alt3: the boy being pulled to the surface by the hook
alt4: two kids walking and eating ice cream, one kid doesn’t realize yet that his ice cream has been hooked
